, 봉침, 약침, 한약, 보약, 공진단, 경옥고 - 원장 소개 * 문학진 원장 - 경희대학교 한의학 박사 - 경희대학교 외래교수 - 전) 청구경희한의원 원장 - 전) 경희대학교 겸임교수 - 척추 신경추나의학회 회원 - 대한응용근신...</p>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-url\">booking.naver.com</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_oglink\", \"id\" :\"SE-062e6766-f3f4-4238-b44d-ab5d42a7f824\", \"data\" : {\"link\" : \"https://booking.naver.com/booking/13/bizes/331349\", \"isVideo\" : \"false\", \"thumbnail\" : \"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fldb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F20210712_178%2F16260891107746eAQY_JPEG%2FWO0W5256_R.jpg%3Ftype%3Df804_408_60_sharpen%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff500_300\"}}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e8504c53-3387-4c3b-aaf9-02d18f7610b3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-981b55a7-2478-44c1-ac26-0abb5d7b69d4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2824f821-4e41-43ec-8693-ad5a2d0da4ac\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b35fbd08-e729-4d0b-b7b6-2ebac1809603\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-df8d7cf6-d8ee-440f-b3ad-450e86b2dc8e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-oglink se-l-image\" id=\"SE-1863f7b4-8553-4